'''第4太陽週期'''是從1755年開始紀錄太陽黑子活動以來的第4個[[太陽週期|太陽週期]] <ref name="Kane">Kane, R.P. (2002). "[http://www.springerlink.com/content/qtq52nl8vtq7w2t6/ Some Implications Using the Group Sunspot Number Reconstruction] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20121204174904/http://www.springerlink.com/content/qtq52nl8vtq7w2t6/ |date=2012-12-04 }}". ''Solar Physics'' '''205(2)''', 383-401.</ref><ref name=SpaceToday>{{cite web | title=The Sun: Did You Say the Sun Has Spots? | url=http://www.spacetoday.org/SolSys/Sun/Sunspots.html | publisher=Space Today Online | accessdate=12 August 2010 | archive-date=2017-07-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170722010544/http://www.spacetoday.org/SolSys/Sun/Sunspots.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個週期開始於1784年9月，結束於1798年5月，持續了13.7年。在這個週期內的最大平滑黑子數(超過12個月期間的黑子月平均數值)為141.1，最小的數值為3.2<ref name="SIDC Monthly Smoothed Sunspot Number">SIDC Monthly Smoothed Sunspot Number. "[http://sidc.oma.be/sunspot-data/] {{Wayback|url=http://sidc.oma.be/sunspot-data/ |date=20140328111426 }}"</ref>。

近來對第4太陽週期有一些猜測，因為他是自1755年以來最長的一個太陽週期，實際上可能是兩個週期<ref>{{cite journal|title=A Solar Cycle Lost in 1793-1800: Early Sunspot Observations Resolve the Old Mystery|journal=The Astrophysical Journal Letters|volume=700|issue=2|pages=L154|url=http://stacks.iop.org/1538-4357/700/i=2/a=L154|date=2009|doi=10.1088/0004-637x/700/2/l154|issn=1538-4357|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Ilya G. Usoskin, Kalevi Mursula, Rainer Arlt, Gennady A. Kovaltsov}}</ref><ref>[http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg20327194.400 "Centuries-old sketches solve sunspot mystery"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg20327194.400 |date=20150402134550 }}, ''New Scientist'', 1 Aug. 2009, p. 10.</ref>。

